description: LA Surf Bot can check the current surf conditions, including wind and tide, at four of LA's top surf spots: County Line, El Porto, Malibu and Venice Beach.
exampleInteractions: Alexa ask LA Surf Bot how's the surf at Malibu
Alexa ask LA Surf Bot how are the waves at Venice
Alexa ask LA Surf Bot what are the conditions at Porto
name: LA Surf Bot
shortDescription: Ask LA Surf Bot for current conditions, including wind and tide, at top LA surf spots.
